    },
    {
      "heading": null,
      "description": "Grab some glasses or jars and start layering up. Spoon a little of the oat mixture into the bottom of your glasses, followed by a spoonful of the toffee sauce and a few banana slices. Repeat the layers in each glass until everything is used up. \nTop each with a dollop of Greek yoghurt (if using) and a scattering of granola. Pop in the fridge overnight, ready for tomorrow's breakfast."
